+Subject: [PATCH 1/6] feat: add Cyrillic support to slugification
+MIME-Version: 1.0
+Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
+Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
+
+Extend SLUGIFY_KEEP_RE and SLUG_SEGMENT_PATTERN with Cyrillic
+range U+0400-U+04FF so files with Cyrillic names produce
+non-empty slugs (e.g. Инфосэл → инфосэл).
+
+just4honey/gbrain fork — local patch.
+---
+ gbrain-weekly-upgrade.sh | 155 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+ run-gbrain.sh            |  16 ++++
